title: Frank Lloyd Wright Ornament—Luxfer Prism
description:
Get in the holiday spirit with this elegant, architectural, and light-as-air ornament inspired by a classic design that Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867–1959) made for the American Luxfer Prism Company in Chicago.  Made of laser-etched brass with a shiny palladium finish in the USA  

3 ¾ x 3 ¾ in.
